I"<p>This works if you want to move a running process to a <em>Tmux</em>  session (requires <code class="highlighter-rouge">reptyr</code>):</p>

<ol>
  <li>Suspend process: press <code class="highlighter-rouge">Ctrl+Z</code></li>
  <li>Resume process in background: <code class="highlighter-rouge">bg</code></li>
  <li>Disown process: <code class="highlighter-rouge">disown %1</code></li>
  <li>Launch <em>Tmux</em></li>
  <li>Find PID: <code class="highlighter-rouge">ps a | grep &lt;$PROCESS_NAME&gt;</code></li>
  <li>Resume process in <em>Tmux</em>: <code class="highlighter-rouge">reptyr &lt;$PID&gt;</code></li>
</ol>

